nmaterial property data can influence the simulation results, and introduce the\nprincipal ideas behind MASTO. This work serves as the reference document for\nciting MASTO when it is used in simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jan 2018 08:51:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
