mon length (overlap) distribution is also considered. We\nprovide a traveling-wave equation derivation of the LFT predictions announced\nin a precedent work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Jan 2018 14:11:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-18"}
